ActCanadian Wheat Board (Interim Operations) Act
SubjectCanadian Wheat Board (Interim Operations) Regulations
PrecisCANADIAN WHEAT BOARD (INTERIM OPERATIONS) REGULATIONS in order to replace the outdated Canadian Wheat Board Regulations, amend the designated barley grade names to match the Canadian Grain Commission's updated Grain Grading Guide, and as a housekeeping measure, repeal spent sets of regulations related to electing the Canadian Wheat Board directors and the Canadian Wheat Board's contingency fund, which are now spent.
